<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us-KR Techno</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="x-icon" href="./css/logo.png">  
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap");

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html,body{
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #003366, #004080, #0059b3, #0073e6);
    }

    body,
    input,
    textarea {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .about-section {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px 1px rgba(0, 1, 3, 0.9);
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 820px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      color: #0f77de;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .about-section p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-section .highlight {
      color: #0f77de;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.6rem 1.3rem;
      background-color: #0f77de;
      border: 2px solid #0f77de;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      border-radius: 25px;
      outline: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #0f77de;
    }
    .menu-btn {
       display: none;
       font-size: 24px;
       cursor: pointer;
       color: #fff;
       background: none;
       border: none;
    }

    /* Header styles */
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      color: #fff;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index:12;
      {{!-- background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); --}}
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    /* Navigation bar styles */
    nav {
      text-align: right;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    nav ul li {
      margin-left: 20px;
    }

    /* Navigation bar link styles */
    nav ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      color: #fca37b;
    }

    footer {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav ul {
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        width: 100%;
        position: absolute;
        top: 60px;
        left: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      header{
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      }
      header h1{
        font-size: 30px;
      }
      nav ul.active {
        display: flex;
        
      }

      nav ul li {
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .menu-btn {
        display: block;
          
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #fff;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 20px;
      }
      footer {
    padding: 5px;
    position: relative;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
  }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .about-section {
        padding: 1.7rem 1.6rem;
      }

      .about-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .about-section p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 0.45rem 1.2rem;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .menu-btn {
        display: block;
          
        font-size: 24px;
           color: #fff;
         background: none;
         border: none;
         cursor: pointer;
         position: absolute;
         top: 10px;
         right: 20px;
      } 
      footer {
    padding: 5px;
    position: relative;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
  }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
 {{>header}}

  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>About KR Techno</h2>
      <p>
        At <span class="highlight">KR Techno</span>, we specialize in providing top-notch technology solutions that cater to the diverse needs of our clients. Our team of dedicated professionals is committed to delivering innovative and efficient solutions to help businesses achieve their goals.
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="highlight">Our Vision </span>Embark on a transformative journey with our software company, committed to shaping a future where technological solutions break boundaries, empowering individuals and organizations to thrive in an interconnected world. We invite you to join us in crafting a visionary landscape where seamless, impactful software experiences become the driving force behind positive change and continuous innovation. Together, let's build a future where technology not only meets expectations but exceeds them, contributing to a world where the potential of interconnected solutions knows no limits.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our services range from software development to IT consulting, and we are always here to assist you with any technical challenges you may face.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{>footer}}

  <script>
    // JavaScript for menu button toggle
    const menuBtn = document.querySelector('.menu-btn');
    const nav = document.querySelector('nav ul');

    menuBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      nav.classList.toggle('active');
      e.stopPropagation();
    });

    // Close menu when clicking outside
    document.addEventListener('click', () => {
      nav.classList.remove('active');
    });

    // Prevent closing when clicking inside the nav
    nav.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.stopPropagation();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
